[1
Date: Tue, 29 Dec 1998 08:56:25 -0500
From: Chuck Trimarchi <trimarch@wadsworth.org>

According to Childs, J.E., et al, 1997. Surveillance and spatiotemporal
associations of rabies in rodents and lagomorphs in the United States,
1985-1994, J Wildlife Dis, 33(1), pp 20-27: there was one laboratory
confirmed rabid prairie dog in the US during the period evaluated,
occurring in 1986.
--
Chuck Trimarchi
e-mail: trimarch@wadsworth.org
